# Styling & Responsiveness

- Use **CSS Modules** or Tailwind with BEM conventions
- Breakpoints:
  - Mobile: <640px
  - Tablet: 641–1024px
  - Desktop: 1025–1440px
  - Large: >1441px
- Use design tokens for spacing, colors, typography
- All styles must be responsive
- Avoid inline styles unless dynamic
- Ensure WCAG 2.1 AA accessibility
